Available Tools: transfer_stock | receive_shipment | adjust_inventory | get_receiving_log
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "sku": "string", "from_location": "string", "to_location": "string", "quantity": number, "reason": "string" }
Response Schema: { "transaction_id": "string", "sku": "string", "quantity": number, "from": "string", "to": "string", "status": "string" }
---
Question: Dispatch 420 units of SKU-5501 from the central depot WH-C to the local outlet STORE-05 for restocking.
Call: { "func_call": "transfer_stock", "sku": "SKU-5501", "from_location": "WH-C", "to_location": "STORE-05", "quantity": 420, "reason": "Outlet restocking" }
Response: { "transaction_id": "TXN-10001", "sku": "SKU-5501", "quantity": 420, "from": "WH-C", "to": "STORE-05", "status": "completed" }

